(firstQuint)The REALITY Study - Head-to-Head Comparison Between Cypher and Taxus.

 This is a prospective, randomized study conducted at 90 centers in Europe, Latin-America and Asia.

 A total of 1335 patients will be entered into the study and will be randomized on a 1:1 basis to either the sirolimus-eluting or the paclitaxel-eluting stent system.

 All patients will have repeat angiography at eight months and will be followed for 24 months post-procedure.

